Order: Simple Coffee, Milk, Sugar(2)
Cost: $2.9
--- Test 4: Fully loaded coffee ---
Order: Simple Coffee, Milk, Sugar(3), Whip Cream, Caramel
Cost: $4.4
--- Test 5: Different order ---
Order: Simple Coffee, Milk, Whip Cream
Cost: $3.2
Order: Simple Coffee, Whip Cream, Milk
Cost: $3.2
--- Test 6: Text formatting ---
Plain: Hello
Bold: <b>Hello</b>
Bold+Italic: <i><b>Hello</b></i>
All: <u><i><b>Hello</b></i></u>
--- Test 7: Multiple orders ---
Order 3: Simple Coffee, Milk = $2.5
Order 4: Simple Coffee, Sugar(1) = $2.2
Order 5: Simple Coffee, Caramel = $2.6
Total: $7.3
--- Test 8: Deep decoration ---
Order: Simple Coffee, Milk, Whip Cream, Sugar(2), Milk, Sugar(1)
Cost: $4.3
--- Test 9: Type checking ---
Is Coffee: true
Is MilkDecorator: true
Is CoffeeDecorator: true
=== Test 20 Complete ===
